OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,FMore members of a religious group have
OL,8,Fbeen arrested on suspicion of child
OL,9,Fneglect as part of an ongoing
OL,10,Finvestigation.
OL,12,FMore than 500 officers took part in
OL,13,Farrests at addresses linked to the
OL,14,FAhmadi Religion of Peace and Light in
OL,15,FCrewe, Cheshire, on 29 April, as part
OL,16,Fof an investigation into alleged
OL,17,Fsexual abuse, forced marriage, and
OL,18,Fmodern slavery.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
