OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,FAfter concerns were raised about the
OL,8,Fwelfare of children, officers say two
OL,9,Ffurther arrests were made on 20 July.
OL,11,FA Mexican woman, 53, was arrested in
OL,12,FMiddlewich, Cheshire on suspicion of
OL,13,Fhuman trafficking and child neglect.
OL,15,FWhile a 43-year-old British man was
OL,16,Falso arrested in Wilmslow on suspicion
OL,17,Fof child neglect offences and
OL,18,Fattempting to pervert the course of
OL,19,Fjustice.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,FA 43-year-old American woman was also
OL,8,Farrested following a warrant on 29
OL,9,FApril, and she was rearrested on
OL,10,Fsuspicion of attempting to pervert the
OL,11,Fcourse of justice.
OL,13,FAll three suspects have been released
OL,14,Fon bail pending further inquiries.
OL,16,FThe force has applied for a Stalking
OL,17,Fand Trafficking Risk Order (STRO)
OL,18,Fagainst the 53-year-old woman and an
OL,19,Fapplication is to be heard at Chester
OL,20,FMagistrates' Court on 23 July.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,FTwelve other suspects have been
OL,8,Farrested as part of the overall
OL,9,Finvestigation and they are currently
OL,10,Fon conditional bail which prevents
OL,11,Fthem from entering Crewe.
OL,13,FThe religious community was based at a
OL,14,Fformer orphanage Webb House in Crewe,
OL,15,Fwhere about 150 people were believed
OL,16,Fto be living.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,FDetective Inspector Eleanor Atkinson
OL,8,Fsaid: "During our ongoing enquiries
OL,9,Fconcerns have come to light in
OL,10,Frelation to the welfare of the
OL,11,Fchildren at Webb House which has
OL,12,Fresulted in today's arrests.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,364,360,120,260,000,100
PN,36306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F363A1784636313
OL,3,CTwo further suspects arrested
OL,4,Cfollowing serious allegations at a
OL,5,Creligious group
OL,7,F"I understand the concern that these
OL,8,Fnew arrests are likely to cause and I
OL,9,Fwould like to reassure local residents
OL,10,Fthat the appropriate safeguarding
OL,11,Fmeasures have been put in place to
OL,12,Fensure the safety of children who are
OL,13,Fmembers of the group and there is not
OL,14,Fbelieved to be any risk to the wider
OL,15,Fcommunity.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/7
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
